######Using the API#######
1. All the URLs referenced in the documentation have the following base WITH VERSION, LANGUAGE:
https://api.api.ai/v1/query?v=20150910&en=English

2. Using Access Tokens

For each API request, include this HTTP header:

Authorization with the value Bearer {access_token}.
For example:

    Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN


